               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; incipits and headings of the texts; abbreviations; miracle numbers; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of the quire numbers.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Mäṣḥafä śǝrʿat and Introductory exhortation are repeated twice.</note>
                     <note>Significant portions of the text (omissions or amendments?) are written in the margin of fols.9v-10r, 12v-13r.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="253va"/>Fol. 253va:   ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተጽሕፈት፡ በ፫፻ወ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ እንዘ፡ ሹም፡ ወረድ፡ በዘመነ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለንግሥነ፡ በካፋ፡ ወጳጳስነ፡ አባ፡ ክርስተ፡ ዱወሉ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡&lt;...&gt;፡[fol. 253vb] ሰበር፨ ወእመሂቦ፡&lt;...&gt;፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ ወአሜን፨<foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>A part of the colophon has been erased. The date mentioned is 307 year of mercy (= 1731 A.D.); the colophon refers to the donor šum Wäräd, King Bäkaffa (r. 1721-30) and Metropolitan Krǝstodolu (III) (in tenure 1720-35). Their names have been written over erasures.</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
